title: Neff Snowboarding Welcomes Brandon Davis
description:
http://neffheadwear.com/snow

Neff Headwear is pleased to announce that Mammoth shredder Brandon Davis is the newest member of the Neff Outerwear program. 2014 has been a breakout year for Brandon, top ten finishes in events like Dew Tour and X Games and narrowly missing the last spot on the US Olympic Team have really put Brandon as one of the ones to watch in Slopestyle and Halfpipe snowboarding. 18 years young Brandon can be found ripping around Mammoth, winning Rev Tours and watch out for him on every major podium next season. Neff is stoked to have Brandon on board and happy to support him with his snowboarding endeavors. Brandon joins a squad of heavies including Dylan Thompson, Sage Kotsenburg (gloves), Halldor and Eiki Helgason (gloves), Louie Vito, Chas Guldemond, Tim Humphreys, Stevie Bell, E-Man Anderson
